What you'll need to compile/use the package:

Using the package:
	xserver
	libcairo2, libfreetype, libx11, libxft
	xsetbg
	discover

Compiling binaries:
	all: gcc
	write-message: libcairo2-dev libx11-dev freetype6-dev libxft-dev

Patching packages:
	debian-like:
		libx11: "apt-get build-dep libx11-6"
		Xephyr: "apt-get build-dep xserver-xephyr"
		fakeroot
		dpkg

Packaging stuff:
	generic:
		tar, gzip
	ubuntu:
		dpkg
